---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | The Data Governor"
  description="Affiliate disclosure for thedatagovernor.com — we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases."
  canonicalPath="/affiliate-disclosure/"
>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="page-header">
      <a href="/" class="label" style="font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.14em;">The Data Governor</a>
      <h1 class="page-title">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="article-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="page-body prose">
      <p>
        In the interest of full transparency, please be aware that some links on
        <strong>thedatagovernor.com</strong> are affiliate links. This means that if you click on a link
        and make a qualifying purchase, The Data Governor may receive a small commission — at
        <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>What This Means</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate links allow me to earn a small referral fee when you purchase products or services
        I recommend. These commissions help support the cost of running this site and allow me to
        continue creating free content for data professionals.
      </p>

      <h2>My Editorial Standards</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate relationships do <strong>not</strong> influence my editorial content. I only recommend
        products and services that I genuinely believe provide value to data governance and data management
        practitioners. All opinions expressed on this site are my own.
      </p>
      <p>
        I will always disclose when a link is an affiliate link. If I'm ever compensated to write about a
        product or service, that will be clearly noted in the content.
      </p>

      <h2>Amazon Associates</h2>
      <p>
        The Data Governor is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate
        advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising
        and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, please
        <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .article-rule {
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red) 0%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 100%);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .page-body {
    max-width: 740px;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .prose {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .prose h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .prose a { color: var(--red); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--red-dark); }
  .prose strong { font-weight: 700; }
</style>
